    "Id": "vehiclechassisdef_TANK_DESTROYER_SM1A",
    "Name": "SM1A",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>SM1A Tank Destroyer</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Clan</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>8/12 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>165 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe SM Tank Destroyer was created as a fast infighter through a collaboration between Clan Nova Cat and Luthien Armor Works on Irece. This variant swaps out the Ultra AC for an LB-X Autocannon/20 with five tons of ammunition. The weight saved goes towards a Light Active Probe and a Light Machine Gun Array to guide its four Light Machine Guns.",
